This is the Debian GNU/Linux prepackaged version of the rc shell. rc was
written by Byron Rakitzis, and is currently maintained by Toby Goodwin
<toby@paccrat.org>.

The package was downloaded from <http://tobold.org/article/rc>.

The rcshell.vim (syntax highlight for vim) is in public domain.

This package was maintained by:

 - Dale Scheetz <dwarf@polaris.net> (1998-1999);
 - Decklin Foster <decklin@red-bean.com> (2000-2006);
 - Jakub Wilk <jwilk@debian.org> (since 2011).
 - Jakukyo Friel <weakish@gmail.com> (since 2014).

